 and a known strictly increasing function 
\begin_inset Formula $\rho_{21}:\mathbb{R}_{\geq0}\to\mathbb{R}_{\geq0}$
\end_inset

 such that 
\begin_inset Formula $\left\Vert N_{B}\right\Vert \leq\gamma_{1}$
\end_inset

 and 
\begin_inset Formula $\left\Vert \dot{N}_{B}\right\Vert \leq\gamma_{3}+\gamma_{4}\left\Vert z\right\Vert +\rho_{2}\left(\left\Vert z\right\Vert \right)\left\Vert z\right\Vert $
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $\forall t\in\mathbb{R}_{\geq0}$
\end_inset

.
