\begin_inset Formula $(a,b,v,w)\in\mathbb{R}^{n}\times\mathbb{R}^{n}\times\mathbb{R}^{m}\times\mathbb{R}^{m}$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $\left\Vert \widetilde{N}\right\Vert \leq\gamma_{2}\left\Vert z\right\Vert +\rho_{1}\left(\left\Vert z\right\Vert \right)\left\Vert z\right\Vert ,\,\forall t\in\mathbb{R}_{\geq0}$
\end_inset

, according to the Mean Value Theorem-based inequality in 
\begin_inset CommandInset citation
LatexCommand cite
after "Lemma 5"
key "arxivKamalapurkar.Klotz.ea2013"
literal "false"

