, where 
\begin_inset Formula $\gamma_{2}\in\mathbb{R}_{\geq0}$
\end_inset

 is a known constant, and 
\begin_inset Formula $\rho_{1}:\mathbb{R}_{\geq0}\to\mathbb{R}_{\geq0}$
\end_inset

 is a known strictly increasing function.
