), respectively,
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{eqnarray}
P & = & \beta\left\Vert e\right\Vert _{1}-e^{T}N_{B}\nonumber \\
 &  & +\mathrm{e}^{-\lambda_{P}t}*\left((\alpha-\lambda_{P})\left(\beta\left\Vert e\right\Vert _{1}-e^{T}N_{B}\right)+e^{T}\dot{N}_{B}\right)\nonumber \\
 &  & +\mathrm{e}^{-\lambda_{P}t}*\left(\left(\gamma_{4}+\rho_{2}\left(\left\Vert z\right\Vert \right)\right)\left\Vert z\right\Vert \left\Vert e\right\Vert _{1}\right),\label{eq:P_expand}
